        <h2>Corporate Clients</h2>

        <p>Dr. Lavian is an expert in <a href="/communications-expert-witness/telecommunications-expert/">telecommunications</a>, network <a href="/communications-expert-witness/network-communications-expert-witness/">communications</a>, and internet technologies. He has a deep understanding of these complex fields. He has worked with some of the biggest names in the industry, including Google, Facebook, Apple, Microsoft, Amazon, LinkedIn, Netflix, Arista, Huawei, ZTE, Cisco, and Juniper.</p>

        <p>Dr. Lavian has helped these companies tackle complex technology challenges. He is known for his ability to stay current with the latest developments in these fields and translate complex technical concepts into language non-experts can understand. His clients highly respect Dr. Lavian for his knowledge, expertise, and ability to deliver real value through his work.</p>

